<div type="translation" resp="part:emfr">
         	
         	<p n="1">
         		Prosperity! Fortune!
         	</p>
         	<p n="1-2">
         		Second year of the victorious king Nirupatoṅkaṉ.<note>Sanskrit Nṛpatuṅga.</note>
         	</p>
         	<p n="2-5">
         		<supplied reason="subaudible">There are</supplied> seven hundred fifty goats
         		that
         		Kārikuṭaiyār, <supplied reason="subaudible">one among</supplied> We the officials <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>atikārikaḷ-ōm</foreign></supplied>,
         		gave 
         		for a perpetual lamp
         		for the god of the glorious <foreign>mūlatāṉam</foreign><note>Sanskrit <foreign>mūlasthāna</foreign>.</note>
         		in Cēntamaṅkalam in the Pāṉaiyūrnāṭu. 
         	</p>
         </div>
      	
